research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Premont city, TX were identified primarily from the Texas Municipal League (TML) City Officials Directory. There was a minor discrepancy with the Texas State Directory Online regarding the Mayor Pro Tem role, with TML listing Irma Martinez as Mayor Pro Tem, Place 2, and the Texas State Directory listing Christen E. Munoz as Mayor Pro Tem. The TML directory was prioritized due to its detailed 'Place' designations for all council members. Only elected positions were included, excluding appointed roles such as City Secretary or Chief of Police.
